  m_text: Yesterday, I went for my routine patient visit. The patient was a very
    cute little girl. She said her grandfather often came to play with her. He slept
    in the bed next to hers, which made her feel less lonely. But I found out that
    the grandfather who slept in the next bed had passed away some time ago.
